                        <interp inst="t18411025-name-1195" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN MOSELEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am clerk of this Court under Mr. Clark. A person named Benjamin Burrows has pleaded guilty to stealing a watch from the prosecutor.</p>
